text.tspan: C.O.D.E is a special project developed by a group of students who studies
diploma in programming at Polytechnic Muadzam Shah. Calling themselves as
a Knight's Code, they produce C.O.D.E as one interactive product for learning C
+ + programming language and it suitable for schools or IPTA students.
Knight's Code is is the pioneer who developed a number of special projects such
as interactive learning, website, android application and system. Acting as a
beginner programming who is trying to develop new products, they produce
products with dedication, discipline, incorporating an attractive design as well
as quality graphics that can be trusted.
